Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:19.81,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}实在过于喜欢 同时伴随些许痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:27.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}由于无法停止已经开始厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:36.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即便在重要的你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:47.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}收入眼底的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:52.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不可能尽然相同
