Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:07.84,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(632,271.333)\fad(400,0)\blur1}三年四班  III
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我看到的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚诞生的新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对无法进入那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.16,0:00:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要创造新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将一切终结
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  艾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…蒂伊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了  将所有的事都告诉亚利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他产生循环的原因  还有我已经死去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后我想了很多  终于决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  艾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我隐瞒了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  蒂伊你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚也跟亚利斯说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「有事想告诉你  过来一趟」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能答应我一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望艾也能在场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂伊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我向亚利斯坦白的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望艾也在场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先去后院的篮球场那等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快就会过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  你也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是说什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算叫她别卖关子快点说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙也是不会说的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是想正式地向你说明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  是跟循环有关的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…我不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请去问蒂伊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  大伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  来的真晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  亚利斯和艾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂伊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细看着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  我怎么睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么了啊  穆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧  很奇怪对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法理解对吧  不可思议对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部  全部都告诉你们好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  大家都是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是忘记了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来帮大家回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂伊真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说了那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个不可思议的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这样的家伙  我还是第一次遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日的时候也是  被你说服了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好弱啊  我真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么面对你时  我总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请不要说什么只对我这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有心事的话  向大家说明就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家肯定会听的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个不可思议的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  回想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浮现出来了吧  想起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无论如何都无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想面对现实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了好多…好多血
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想说那不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…许下了愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候  在夕阳下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许下了愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俯视着尸体  许下了愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请当一切都没发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请将原来的欢乐时光还给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让它永远永远持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的愿望如果是让他复活就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  大家不约而同地祈愿了「永远」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也是一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可却回想起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想重新来过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想忘记了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将那天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  再一次重新来过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从最初开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是蒂伊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙  想将这个世界整个重置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙一定会将整个四班的记忆限制解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空间无法承受矛盾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  招牌上的字是不是写错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真的  是谁写的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  忘记拿发票了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班长  有什么办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自…自掏腰包…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要重置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论这个世界  或是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疤面！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:10:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小镇被雾吞没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是他说过的重置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这14年与亚利斯度过的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有只有我知道的亚利斯的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  我要重新来过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会像那时一样坠下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一样死去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛地撞击到地面上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支离破碎到无法作为死者复活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在消散
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总算明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是蒂伊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是亚利斯…对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我想救蒂伊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果自己掉了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摔死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么久了都没让你察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我做梦也没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然会误认为死掉的是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:13:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不想消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一直以来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的…亚利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到外面的世界去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有亚利斯的话就不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重置呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家再重置一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做的话  不就让这一切都化为泡影了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一起去外面的世界  四处旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时而争吵  时而欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切的一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不都会化为泡影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你们度过的这一年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不也一样会消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你们出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了外面后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长到17岁  18岁  19岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年都迎接自己的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大后…也要记得我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔能想起就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来  我就能永远和你们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一生永相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…不应该还有别的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让亚利斯也一起到外面去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾  那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为亚利斯就是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍己为人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便知道自己会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利斯也会选择拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  蒂伊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时和我一起去到外面的…一起旅行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过那里就是原本的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穆  你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会忘记你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能答应我一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗耳恭听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么来的就怎么进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是重置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…整个小镇正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:19:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩也赶紧来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先带赛莉卡去安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾一定不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快  你也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得在葛拉学园的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你说过关于观察者的那番话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界的观察者只剩你一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你走就能终结一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个残忍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来带我来这个世界是为了让我抹消你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真残忍  太残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利斯  你想和大家一起活下去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想长到17岁的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想独自消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话啊  亚利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的  我在14年前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面的世界有我的坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那被守墓人正式埋葬了的遗体正沉睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我想拯救…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我想拯救…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利斯的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被世界拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:21:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.35,0:23:08.32,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}<亚利斯·卡勒>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
